OL,3,CVaping to be banned in cars carrying
OL,4,Cchildren under government plans
OL,6,FVaping will be banned in cars carrying
OL,7,Fchildren, according to new government
OL,8,Fproposals.
OL,10,FPeople will be prevented from smoking,
OL,11,Fvaping or using devices that heat
OL,12,Ftobacco in children's playgrounds,
OL,13,Foutside schools and in cars carrying
OL,14,Fyoungsters, according to the plan,
OL,15,Fwhich is subject to consultation.
OL,17,FThe Department of Health said the move
OL,18,Fto extend smoke-free places would
OL,19,Fprotect children and vulnerable
OL,20,Fpeople, including from the harms of
OL,21,Fbreathing in secondhand smoke.
