OL,3,CVaping to be banned in cars carrying
OL,4,Cchildren under government plans
OL,6,FIt would mean smoking is banned
OL,7,Foutside hospitals and other health
OL,8,Ffacilities, though vaping would still
OL,9,Fbe allowed there in a bid to support
OL,10,Fsmokers who are trying to quit.
OL,12,FAll existing indoor places where
OL,13,Fsmoking is already banned will become
OL,14,F"heated tobacco-free and vape-free",
OL,15,Fincluding workplaces, public transport
OL,16,Fand private vehicles carrying under-
OL,17,F18s.
