OL,6,FOutdoor areas near hospitality venues,
OL,7,Fsuch as bar, pub and restaurant
OL,8,Fgardens, will be exempt from the ban,
OL,9,Falongside "wide-open public spaces"
OL,10,Fincluding beaches.
OL,12,FPeople would continue to be able to
OL,13,Fchoose whether to smoke or vape in
OL,14,Ftheir homes or in private outdoor
OL,15,Fspaces.
OL,17,FHealth Secretary Wes Streeting said:
OL,18,F"No child in a playground or hospital
OL,19,Fpatient should suffer because someone
OL,20,Felse chooses to smoke.
