OL,6,F"Secondhand smoke increases the risk
OL,7,Fof heart disease and lung cancer and
OL,8,Fwe want to protect children and the
OL,9,Fsick from harm.
OL,11,F"Prevention is better than cure, so
OL,12,Fthis government is taking pressure off
OL,13,Fthe NHS and building a healthier
OL,14,FBritain where everyone lives well for
OL,15,Flonger."
OL,17,FAccording to the Department of Health,
OL,18,Fthe consultation marks an "important
OL,19,Fstep" towards implementing the Tobacco
OL,20,Fand Vapes Bill, which is progressing
OL,21,Fthrough Parliament.
