OL,6,F"The health risks are greatest for
OL,7,Fchildren, pregnant women and people
OL,8,Fwith medical conditions. No smoker
OL,9,Fwants to harm people, but with
OL,10,Fsecondhand smoke they do ` and these
OL,11,Fmeasures would reduce the harm
OL,12,Fsecondhand smoke causes the most
OL,13,Fmedically vulnerable in our society."
OL,15,FThe consultation will look at how
OL,16,Foutdoor boundaries will be set
OL,17,Falongside possible exemptions, with
OL,18,Fthe intention of making the rules
OL,19,Fproportionate and workable, the
OL,20,FDepartment of Health said.
