OL,6,FBritish Heart Foundation chief
OL,7,Fexecutive Dr Charmaine Griffiths said:
OL,8,F"No child should have to walk through
OL,9,Fa cloud of deadly secondhand smoke on
OL,10,Ftheir way to the classroom or
OL,11,Fplayground, nor should any patient be
OL,12,Fexposed to harm on hospital grounds.
OL,14,F"We strongly support the government's
OL,15,Fconsultation and the landmark
OL,16,Flegislation behind it, and we call for
OL,17,Furgent implementation to protect
OL,18,Feveryone from harm."
